  <brief_title>Feasibility of a Modular mHealth for Tailored Rehabilitation of Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>MMHTR</acronym>
  <official_title>Feasibility of a Modular mHealth for Tailored Rehabilitation During the Treatment of Breast Cancer</official_title>
